msgid "KTeaTime"
msgstr "KTeaTime"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kteatime.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Tea Cooker"
msgstr "Kuhalnik čaja"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kteatime.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KTeaTime is a handy timer for steeping tea. No longer will you have to guess "
"at how long it takes for your tea to be ready. Simply select the type of tea "
"you have, and it will alert you when the tea is ready to drink."
msgstr ""
"KTeaTime je priročen časomer za namakanje čaja. Nič več vam ne bo treba "
"ugibati, kako dolgo bo trajalo, preden bo vaš čaj gotov. Enostavno izberite "
"vrsto čaja, ki ga imate, in opozorjeni boste, ko bo čaj pripravljen za pitje."
